tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE golf_equipment (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  club_type VARCHAR(255),
  brand VARCHAR(255),
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  in_stock BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE clubs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(255),
    type VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    availability BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE balls (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(255),
    color VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    availability BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE accessories (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    category VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    availability BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE clubs (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  brand VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  availability BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE balls (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  brand VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  color VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  availability BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE accessories (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  type VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT NOT NULL,
  availability BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT NOT NULL,
  product_id INT NOT NULL,
  quantity INT NOT NULL,
  order_date DATE NOT NULL,
  delivery_date DATE,
  status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE clubs ( 
  club_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
  club_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, 
  club_type VARCHAR(50), 
  club_price DECIMAL(10, 2), 
  club_stock INTEGER 
);

CREATE TABLE balls ( 
  ball_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
  ball_brand VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, 
  ball_type VARCHAR(50), 
  ball_price DECIMAL(10, 2), 
  ball_stock INTEGER 
);

CREATE TABLE accessories ( 
  accessory_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
  accessory_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, 
  accessory_type VARCHAR(50), 
  accessory_price DECIMAL(10, 2), 
  accessory_stock INTEGER 
);

CREATE TABLE orders ( 
  order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, 
  customer_id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
  order_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, 
  total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2), 
  FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id) 
);
